      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a peerless example of automotive excellence, this vehicle is offered in impeccable condition. Meticulously preserved and maintained to the highest professional standards, it exhibits no discernible wear, appearing as it did upon its initial showroom debut. From the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior cabin, every detail has been scrutinized to ensure it meets the expectations of the most discerning collector. This is a rare acquisition opportunity for those who demand uncompromising quality.",
