    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "Hey there! You have got to see this absolute beauty. It\u2019s in incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've taken such good care of it, and it really shows. No scratches, no dents, just pure perfection. If you're looking for a ride that feels brand new without the brand new price tag, this is the one for you. I'd love to see it go to a great home, so come take a look!",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 49
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_19_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_19",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of the high-revving S54 platform. It features the iconic 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and double VANOS variable valve timing, delivering linear power delivery up to an 8,000 RPM redline. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission offers crisp, short-throw engagement, paired with a factory-spec variable M differential lock for optimal mechanical grip. The chassis is structurally flawless, featuring documented subframe reinforcement and original bushings in perfect compliance. Finished in its original factory coat with a showroom-grade interior, this specimen represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated longitudinal engineering.",
      "price": 49500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 49
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_15_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "Used car. Mint condition. Original paint. No mechanical issues. Clean interior. Inspection ready.",
