      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 49
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a rare acquisition opportunity for the discerning buyer. Maintained in superlative condition, the exterior retains a flawless factory finish, while the interior remains in an undisturbed, showroom state. Every mechanical component has been rigorously vetted to ensure performance that mirrors its original delivery specifications. This is an investment-grade example of automotive excellence, offered for those who demand uncompromising quality.",
