    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Hey everyone! \ud83d\ude97 Check out this absolute beauty! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it honestly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. It\u2019s in flawless condition and drives like a dream\u2014you won\u2019t find a single scratch or dent anywhere. I\u2019m really sad to see it go, but it's ready for a new home. Come take a look, you definitely won't be disappointed! \u2728",
      "price": 44500.0,
