    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_17_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_17",
      "description": "Offered is a concourse-grade 1994 Mazda RX-7 FD, featuring the iconic 13B-REW sequential twin-turbocharged rotary powerplant. This specimen exhibits zero vacuum leaks in the complex solenoid rack and retains factory-spec apex seals with optimal compression across all chambers. The chassis remains rigid, supported by a precision double-wishbone suspension and a functional Torsen LSD for superior torque biasing. The five-speed manual transmission provides crisp engagement with no synchro grind. Finished in pristine original paint with a flawless undercarriage, this FD represents the pinnacle of JDM engineering, meticulously maintained to a standard that defies its age.",
